<br>
    Zellex , as far as I know is probably one of the most imformative people in a raid I know and of corse whenever he can , I would utilize him for pulling and FDing with the occasional other monk following him around to see how to do it and learn just in case we dont have zellex on a raid. <br>
<br>
    I'm not quite sure you read the whole thing bro but if you see there. I said that of corse whenever I could use him bro. I did'nt make it sound like I was commanding him to be there at every raid. I mean I can be very resouceful when I need to be and with the friends i have that are still wearing SF tags and alot of them in Paralax now I'm sure I can get something going when I need to for a raid. <br>
<br>
    It also seems as if things in the past are coming back to haunt me when the events happened at times when i was very young in the game and did'nt know much about raiding at all. If you have any doubts on wheather or not I've helped anyone. You can ask any CoM member and they will tell you I have helped CoM greatly. After all , I did solo 57 , Every little blue line in it outside rygor fort and I gave away at least about 12 to 20 FULL SETS of rygor armor to my guildmates and to others in the zone that were'nt even part of CoM. I would get a piece and TP to a ring near them and run to them and give it to them and then gate back to my bind outside the fort. <br>
<br>
     Ask Lexi if I gave her a blue diamond bracer for a res ( and this is not the first time I've done this ). I've been anything but harmful for the majority of my 110 days played on Mechy. I have had a couple instances that were considered not very honerable. They were both a very long time ago. I believe that DN raid you were reffering to was last year as a matter of fact. Then again , what person that has played this game has played it 100 percent correct and not been an ass to anyone for the whole time they have played? You find one person that has done that and show me proof and I'll give them 1kpp. Its just not possible. <br>
